race.comment: The leading stable holds the aces. BOLDINHO (1) was heavily bet again delivering the hat-trick comfortably. Finally has an inside gate and he is well-placed to go on with the job. Stablemate FLYING ANNIE (3) led against the above first-up and fought on beaten 1L. She presents fitter and will likely push forward again. Will prove tough to beat. CONVINCEBILITY (4) missed a nose and then delivered the win both at 70 level. That form stacks up and he will get every chance. FIELD OF FLUTES (2) has been plainer since the win in this grade three back. On song he can get some of the minor purse. NO BRAKES (5) needs to lift to be competitive.
